==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Manslaughter
<hw>Man"slaugh`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
slaying of a human being; destruction of men.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>The unlawful killing of a man,
either in negligence or incidentally to the commission of some unlawful
act, but without specific malice, or upon a sudden excitement of
anger.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Manslayer</ent>⟦br⟧
